data.description: Still under builder warranty! When you enter this immaculately kept, second-home owner, barely lived in home you are greeted by an elongated foyer, perfect for greeting guests. This Buffington home,  Caldwell plan offers an open floorplan with plenty of natural sunlight and smooth flow that seamlessly opens up to the living room and dining area. The spacious kitchen features granite counters, custom  made cabinets with tons of storage space, breakfast bar and stainless steel appliances. Ample granite, counterspace allows for your chef inspired meals to come to life while the open kitchen concept allows for entertaining while hosting and prepping meals. Dining  area is open and spacious enough to seat up to 10 people. Master bedroom is tucked away from the additional bedrooms, the master suite boasts plenty of natural light with views into the large back yard. The en-suite master bath showcases a dual-sink vanity, separate walk-in shower with built in bench, soaker tub with jets and spacious walk-in closet.  The backyard is leveled with full sprinkler system and blooming trees and can still use your green thumb for customization! Relax on the covered back patio and enjoy this beautiful property. If your in the mood for outdoor fun- come out and enjoy your resort style amenity center with plenty of activities to choose from and enjoy! Community is centrally located to major fwy's, shopping centers(San Marcos Outlet Mall!), dining, outdoor adventures, San Marcos river, Texas State University and more. This retreat is the perfect location between Austin and San Antonio!  **HOUSE IS ALSO AVAILABLE FOR LEASE AT $1995 A MONTH**
